{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund student support centres in every school",
        "additional_details": "This could help students feel safer going to school across the country and, being based in school, would have good connections with teachers and would be more able to help solve the problem. I would like this to happen as it could help students who are struggling with school feel safer and calmer knowing they could go there when they needed it.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to fund Student Support Centres in every school. [We believe that] Student Support Centres could be there to help students with safeguarding and mental health.",
